^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now, let's analyze the bidding a bit first, and then the play. Should Elizabeth bid 2N or 3N? Using Bergen method she has nine HCP, one length point, and one quality suit point. So, 3N is a good bid with her hand. Next, let's analyze the play. |
