^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Moe has one spades, two club, and two diamonds off the top. So, he needs four extra tricks in the red suits. Attacking hearts was a reasonable idea, as even worst case, he is likely to take 3 hearts. So, I would play the first two tricks as he did, and then lead a diamond to the Ace and another heart. I would play low on the second heart as well. Against really expert defenders, it is hard to say whether to play the King or 10, as a world class North would duck the first heart, even with the Ace.|
